# Input

```svelte
<!-- if / else-if / else -->
{#if porridge.temperature > 100}
	<p>too hot!</p>
{:else if 80 > porridge.temperature}
	<p>too cold!</p>
{:else if 100 > porridge.temperature}
	<p>too too cold!</p>
{:else}
	<p>just right!</p>
{/if}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
<!-- if / else-if / else -->
{#if porridge.temperature > 100}
	<p>too hot!</p>
{:else if 80 > porridge.temperature}
	<p>too cold!</p>
{:else if 100 > porridge.temperature}
	<p>too too cold!</p>
{:else}
	<p>just right!</p>
{/if}

```
